Now the big question is,
what the hell
we gonna mash in?

35:15.614 --> 35:16.880
We'll come up with something.

35:16.882 --> 35:18.615
We're gonna have to figure it
out pretty quickly.

35:18.617 --> 35:20.951
Gonna have to get
mashed in
in the next few days.

35:20.953 --> 35:23.353
We're at that point,
and we're ready.
Right? That's a start.

35:23.355 --> 35:25.021
We got the wheels a-turning.

35:25.023 --> 35:27.591
We got the site for it, now.
We got good, clean,
fresh water.

35:27.593 --> 35:29.159
Good damn job today.

35:29.161 --> 35:30.727
It felt pretty good today,
to get here and work.

35:30.729 --> 35:33.230
Yeah! I'm tickled with it!

35:33.232 --> 35:35.398
<i> [jerry] I don't know</i>
<i>  about you, but I'm ready</i>
<i>  for a burger.</i>

35:45.677 --> 35:49.279
<i> [ramsey] you know,</i>
<i>  I don't know if this cherry</i>
<i>  will be cognac, technically.</i>

35:49.281 --> 35:51.481
