<i> [digger] we'll tell it</i>
<i>  long enough, it'll believe</i>
<i>  anything we tell it.</i>

35:53.785 --> 35:55.185
<i> [richard] back in paradise.</i>

35:55.187 --> 35:59.156
The day has come.
It's time to run
hillbilly cajun cognac.

35:59.158 --> 36:01.091
[richard] lookee, there.

36:02.895 --> 36:04.494
Oh, hell.

36:04.496 --> 36:06.563
It's better than last year's
calendar, ain't it?

36:06.565 --> 36:09.266
Mash is wonderful.
