-Smells pretty good.
-Hmm.

36:15.073 --> 36:18.275
Let's make some damn
hillbilly cajun cognac
right quick.

36:18.277 --> 36:20.610
Yeah, let's get busy
of getting her preheated.

36:20.612 --> 36:22.112
If we can get
some of these flavors

36:22.114 --> 36:24.447
to come through
in this end run,
