you turning

36:28.620 --> 36:31.821
-that damn condenser on.
-[digger] keep your head
kind of out of the way.

36:31.823 --> 36:34.891
Unless you like looking
at flames right before
they set your eyes on fire.

36:34.893 --> 36:36.493
You ready?

36:36.495 --> 36:38.361
[digger] well, no,
but the question is,
are you ready?

36:38.797 --> 36:40.230
Whoa!

36:45.671 --> 36:48.071
[ramsey] right here
is where the old man's at,
richard.

36:48.073 --> 36:50.874
[digger] yep.
Don't look like he's dug out,
yet.

36:50.876 --> 36:52.976
I wouldn't put it
past him, though.

36:52.978 --> 36:53.777
[richard] he try
to get out of there?

36:53.779 --> 36:55.512
-[ramsey] oh, yeah.
-[digger] yeah.

36:55.514 --> 36:58.048
He ain't never been one
for conforming to the rules.
You ought to know that.

36:58.050 --> 37:00.917
