I would see this
in my lifetime.

37:00.919 --> 37:03.653
Yeah, he's a... He's there.

37:03.655 --> 37:06.723
[ramsey] he's actually buried
about eight or nine feet deep.

37:06.725 --> 37:09.893
[digger] it's as deep
