37:09.895 --> 37:12.128
[mark] hell, we wouldn't want
to give him a chance
to claw out.

37:12.130 --> 37:13.763
-[richard chuckles]
-[digger] yep.

37:13.765 --> 37:15.899
Old man, I want you
to meet richard.

37:15.901 --> 37:17.968
Richard, meet popcorn.

